  /*
  newroot = XCreateSimpleWindow(display, root, 50, 50, 300, 300, 3,
          WhitePixelOfScreen(screen), BlackPixelOfScreen(screen));
  frame = XCreateSimpleWindow(display, newroot, 50, 50, 300, 300, 3,
          WhitePixelOfScreen(screen), BlackPixelOfScreen(screen));
  frame2 = XCreateSimpleWindow(display, newroot, 40, 40, 300, 300, 3,
          BlackPixelOfScreen(screen), WhitePixelOfScreen(screen));
  */

  SubstructureRedirectMask for when windows are mapping to redirect them
  EnterWindowMask for turning on the "resize hotspot"
  LeaveWindowMask for turning off the "resize hotspot"
  ButtonPressMask for deselecting windows
  ButtonReleaseMask for deselecting windows/resizing windows?
  XGrabPointer to confine the pointer to a particular area.
  XUngrabPointer
  XNextEvent(display, &event) for asynchronous blocking events.
  XReparentWindow(display, window, parent, rel-x, rel-y);
  XSelectInput(display, window, event_mask) 
    or set attributes on create window.
  
  XMapWindow(display, newroot);
  XMapWindow(display, frame);
  XMapWindow(display, frame2);  
  XReparentWindow(display, frame, frame2, 20, 20);
  

